column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, &&&&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, s.specobjid, p.type, s.class, p.deVRad_r, p.deVRadErr_r, p.expRad_r, p.expRadErr_r, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, g.bptclass, g.lgm_tot_p5#, g.sfr_tot_p5#, g.specsfr_tot_p5#, z.spiral, z.elliptical, z.uncertain FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN photoobj AS p ON p.objID = x.objID JOIN SpecObj as s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN galSpecExtra as g ON g.specobjid = s.specobjid JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = g.specobjid ORDER BY x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
